DataElement.preferredName: Disease or Disorder Condition Reported Date
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Any abnormal condition of the body or mind that causes discomfort, dysfunction, or distress to the person affected or those in contact with the person. The term is often used broadly to include injuries, disabilities, syndromes, symptoms, deviant behaviors, and atypical variations of structure and function.:A state of being, such as a state of health._The date (and time) on which the entity or event is reported.:A state of being, such as a state of health._The date (and time) on which the entity or event is reported._The particular day, month and year an event has happened or will happen.
